      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should talk to my doc but i have an appointment in like 3 weeks and i already feel terrible. if i just stop the sertraline today and start the st johns wort tomorrow, how bad is the interaction actually gonna be? is it like a small thing or should i be worried?",
