      "content": "wait so if it just reduces the effectiveness, that's not like, dangerous right? i'm more worried about like stopping the meds cold turkey. if i just start the st johns wort tomorrow morning, what dose of the herb should i take to make sure i get enough to cover the gap? like how many mg is standard for a replacement?",
